raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Baaabe!
Mabel: Wake upp
Mabel: 🤩
Player: You're excited today 😁
Mabel: Duh!!
Mabel: We have a daaate 🥳🥳
Mabel: Did you forget?
Mabel: img: mabel/58
Player: Of course not 😨
Mabel: Good hehe
Mabel: What's not to be excited about hehe
Player: True!
Player: Any ideas on where you want to go?
do echo_set([\"59\"])
Mabel: Mmmmh...
Mabel: Thought: Where do we go... 
Mabel: Thought: And what should I wear??
Mabel: Thought: Ooh I could wear that new dress!
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Mabel: Thought: No Mabel! Nobody wears dresses in college!!
	Mabel: Thought: Girls are supposed to look more hot and mature
else:
	Mabel: Thought: Or should I wear my older one that I've been saving for a date??
	Mabel: Thought: Or what if someone else is wearing the same dress!?
	Mabel: Thought: I wouldn't look cute anymore... Ok no dress today
Mabel: Hmmm
Player: Any day now is okay!
Mabel: THE PARK!!
do echo_clear()
Mabel: We're going to the park today!
Player: Spoken with a lot of conviction!
Mabel: Mabel has decided 😌
Mabel: Okay I need to get dressed quick!!
Player: So I'll be there in an hour?k
Mabel: Thought: I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO WEAR
Mabel: Uhm.. would 2 hours do? 😇
